title: Raiders-Ravens recap; Roger Goodell; Liar Liar Pants on Fire; Power Rankings
itunes:title: Raiders-Ravens recap; Roger Goodell; Liar Liar Pants on Fire; Power Rankings
description:
In the latest edition of the Good Morning Football Podcast, hosts Kay Adams, Peter Schrager, Kyle Brandt, and Thomas Davis discuss the thrilling Raiders, Ravens game on Monday Night Football; MJ Acosta-Ruiz is joined by commissioner Roger Goodell to talk about the monumental move to NFL LA and week 1; the hosts also dive into NFL power rankings and wise fantasy football waiver wire pickups!

The Good Morning Football Podcast is part of the NFL Podcast Network.
